word field\n84: - [ ] Define agent_endpoint field\n85: - [ ] Implement from_options classmethod\n86: - [ ] Add docstrings for all fields and methods\n87: \n88: **Verification**: Run `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; opts = MetadataOptions.from_options({}); print(opts)\"` and verify it works\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ### Task 6: Implement agentcube/models/metadata.py - AgentMetadata Pydantic model\n93: - [ ] Import BaseModel, Field from pydantic\n94: - [ ] Import Optional from typing\n95: - [ ] Define AgentMetadata class extending BaseModel\n96: - [ ] Define agent_name field with required validation\n97: - [ ] Define description field as Optional[str]\n98: - [ ] Define language field with default \"python\"\n99: - [ ] Define entrypoint field with required validation\n100: - [ ] Define port field with default 8080 and range validation\n101: - [ ] Define build_mode field with default \"local\"\n102: - [ ] Define region field as Optional[str]\n103: - [ ] Define version field as Optional[str]\n104: - [ ] Define requirements_file field as Optional[str]\n105: - [ ] Add validator for language field (must be \"python\" or \"java\")\n106: - [ ] Add validator for build_mode field (must be \"local\" or \"cloud\")\n107: - [ ] Add validator for port field (must be 1-65535)\n108: - [ ] Add comprehensive docstrings\n109: \n110: **Verification**: Run `python -c \"from agentcube.models.metadata import AgentMetadata; m = AgentMetadata(agent_name='test', entrypoint='test'); print(m)\"` and verify it validates correctly\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ### Task 7: Implement agentcube/services/__init__.py - Service initialization\n115: - [ ] Export MetadataService class\n116: - [ ] Add package-level docstring\n117: - [ ] Configure logging for services module\n118: \n119: **Verification**: Run `python -c \"from agentcube.services import MetadataService; print(MetadataService)\"` and verify it imports correctly\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ### Task 8: Imp