{"type":"text","timestamp":1775865976239,"sessionID":"ses_286252d1cffeKPg870jV0WDBP8","part":{"id":"prt_d79dc44cf001ln6aEIGwh4MAmk","messageID":"msg_d79dc2144001hhJWPfKskZyhSx","sessionID":"ses_286252d1cffeKPg870jV0WDBP8","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-020 codebase:\n\n## Completed\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- Full `PackRuntime` class with workspace validation, metadata management, Dockerfile generation for Python/Java\n- `MetadataOptions` dataclass and `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model with validation\n- `MetadataService` for loading/saving metadata files\n- CLI `pack` command with all options (agent-name, language, entrypoint, port, build-mode, description, output, verbose)\n- Project structure with pyproject.toml, README.md\n\n**Testing:**\n- 28 unit tests passing (100% for pack_runtime)\n- 81% coverage on pack_runtime.py\n- Tests for models, metadata service, and pack runtime\n\n**Documentation & Examples:**\n- cmd/cli/README.md with usage examples\n- examples/hello-agent/ Python workspace example\n\n## Deferred\n\n**Integration/E2E Tests:**\n- Integration tests for Python/Java workspace packing\n- End-to-end test for complete workflow\n- Error handling and verbose mode tests\n- Custom output path tests\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Method docstrings for PackRuntime and MetadataService\n- Java workspace example\n- Troubleshooting section in README\n\n**Code Quality:**\n- PEP 8 style verification (flake8/black)\n- Type hint completeness (mypy)\n- Test coverage >80% (currently 40% overall, 81% for pack_runtime)","time":{"start":1775865976238,"end":1775865976238}}}
